    dc:creator "Kim, Sam-Kyu", "Lee, Jun-Ho" ;
    dc:date "2023" ;
    dc:title "A taxonomic study on the genus Stichillus (Diptera: Phoridae) from South Korea, with a key to species from East Asia" ;
    bibo:endPage "398" ;
    bibo:issue "3" ;
    bibo:journal "Zootaxa" ;
    bibo:pubDate "2023-10-04" ;
    bibo:startPage "381" ;
    bibo:volume "5352" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8407392>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8407394>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8407398>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8407400>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8407404>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8407412> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8407392>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Habitus of Stichillus species from South Korea, lateral view. A, S. cylindratus (male); B, S. cylindratus (female); C, S. japonicus (male); D, S. japonicus (female); E, S. koreanus sp. nov. (male); F, S. koreanus sp. nov. (female); G, S. spinosus (male); H, S. spinosus (female). Scale bars=2 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8407392/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8407394>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Ocellar regions of Stichillus species from South Korea, dorsal view. A, S. cylindratus (male); B, S. cylindratus (female); C, S. japonicus (male); D, S. japonicus (female); E, S. koreanus sp. nov. (male); F, S. koreanus sp. nov. (female); G, S. spinosus (male); H, S. spinosus (female). Scale bars=0.1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8407394/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8407398>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Hind tibiae (A–D) and fore tarsi (E, F) of male Stichillus species from South Korea, dorsal view.A, S. cylindratus; B, E, S. japonicus; C, F, S. koreanus sp. nov.; D, S. spinosus. Abbreviations: f=fusion of setal palisades; sp=setal palisade. Scale bars=0.5 mm (A–D), 0.2 mm (E, F)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8407398/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8407400>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Wings of Stichillus species from South Korea, dorsal view. A, S. cylindratus (male); B, S. cylindratus (female); C, S. japonicus (male); D, S. japonicus (female); E, S. koreanus sp. nov. (male); F, S. koreanus sp. nov. (female); G, S. spinosus (male); H, S. spinosus (female). Scale bars=0.5 mm (A, B, E–H); 1 mm (C, D)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8407400/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8407404>
    dc:description "FIGURE 7. Male hypopygium and femalepostabdomen of Stichillus japonicus, leftview (A, D, F), posterior view (B),right view (C, E) and dorsal view (G). A–C, hypopygium; D, E, aedeagus; F, G, female postabdomen.Abbreviations (A–E): aed=aedeagus; arm=arm on dorsal plate of aedeagus; dp=dorsal plate of aedeagus; ep=epandrium; epl=epandrial lobe; hyp=hypandrium; ip (with white circle)=inner projection of hypandrium; lml=lateral membranous lobe of hypandrium; vm=ventral membrane of aedeagus. Abbreviations (F, G): go=genital opening; s9=sternite 9; sg7=abdominal segment 7; t8=tergite 8; t9=tergite 9. Arrow (A, C): base of inner projection of hypandrium. Scale bars=0.2 mm (A–C, F, G), 0.1 mm (D, E)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8407404/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8407412>
    dc:description "FIGURE 10. Habitats (A, B) and live individuals (C–H) of Stichillus japonicus. A, forest in Mt. Hambaeksan, Changokbong Peak (Jeongseon); B, streamside in Mt. Yeonhwasan (Taebaek); C, female, wandering on leaf of wood fern (Dryopteris crassirhizoma); D, female, wandering on leaf of bamboo (Sasa borealis); E, male, licking bamboo leaf surface; F, female, resting on leaf of shrub; G, female, on rock surface in streamside at night; H, ditto, male." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8407412/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

